            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="Given that the name of the model is S-Doc (strict-doc), it is reasonable to make the document files have the ``.sdoc`` extension. This helps to identify the document files.">
