              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="The relations between all documents are a summary of all relations between these documents&#x27; requirements. This information is useful for:\n\n1) Structural analysis of a requirements/documents graph.\n2) Incremental regeneration of only those documents whose content was modified.">
              <DEFINITION>
