            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="StrictDoc shall support parsing the most commonly used formats and programming languages to the Abstract Syntax Tree (AST) level.\n\nThe format examples: C, C++, Python, Rust, Ada, Robot, Gherkin, etc.">
