              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="A class is a basic building block of most programming language. Some requirements can be naturally attached to the whole classes.">
              <DEFINITION>
                <ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>REQUIREMENT_dc65dfe126e94a7e894ca0421cf6849c_RATIONALE</ATTRIBUTE-DEFINITION-STRING-REF>
