              </DEFINITION>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING>
            <ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-STRING THE-VALUE="StrictDoc shall avoid using large and demanding UI frameworks.\n\nNOTE: An example of frameworks that require a very specific architecture: React JS, AngularJS.">
              <DEFINITION>
